title: Google Fonts
shortDescription: Add free custom fonts to your site.
longDescription: Google Fonts allows you to add unique fonts to your webpage. Give your webpage any feeling from serious to lovable.
instructions: Choose what fonts you want for your headers and main body, and then add fonts to any custom locations from there.
author: Google Inc.
